Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:46.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial Unicode MS\fs75} Ἑρμῆς Τρισμέγιστος{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:51.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说这个谁懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.25,0:16:03.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.93,0:16:07.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你也是以父亲为力量源泉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.17,0:16:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就先从那边下手好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.40,0:16:12.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.77,0:16:35.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里危险　快上车
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.94,0:16:42.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,响
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.67,0:16:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停手吧　卡萝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.23,0:16:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夙愿成真触手可及
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.02,0:16:53.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今岂可半途而废
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.00,0:16:57.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回忆也好什么也好　全都燃烧殆尽也在所不惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.36,0:17:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial Unicode MS}Dur-da-Blá Faust-Robe{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.47,0:17:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这光芒真让人不禁以为这是Symphogear
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.81,0:17:37.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不只是光芒好看而已哦　好好领教一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.92,0:17:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.11,0:17:49.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交战地点的能量压值急速上升
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.64,0:17:53.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对照完成　这个波形是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:56.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然是Phonic Gain
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.70,0:17:59.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是卡萝尔的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.46,0:18:27.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这威力简直就像…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别装傻骗自己了　这就是绝唱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.86,0:18:34.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然毫无负担得唱响绝唱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.12,0:18:37.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼金术这简直是开挂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.07,0:18:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就用S2CA…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.49,0:18:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行　那威力立花你的身体承受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.98,0:18:45.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.34,0:18:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼　你看那里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.80,0:19:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪烁…律动…共振！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.09,0:19:09.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整个城堡就像是音叉一般
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.80,0:19:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与卡萝尔的歌声产生共鸣大幅提升能量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.54,0:19:36.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以放射线状扩散的能量波正沿地表交叉收束
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.48,0:19:38.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这轨迹…难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.06,0:19:40.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Photon Sphere
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.84,0:19:42.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行　这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.56,0:19:48.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了　我不想再对女儿努力的样子佯装视而不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.14,0:19:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让我亲眼目睹女儿…响战斗的样子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.13,0:19:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能量波向对跖点汇聚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.75,0:19:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次向上射出
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.75,0:20:02.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夭寿啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.01,0:20:08.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界将就此分解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.82,0:20:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想得逞…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.70,0:20:18.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是有Armed Gear的话说不定就打中了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.03,0:20:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.02,0:20:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去阻止那个大型装置
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.40,0:20:34.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我们还要依赖LiNKER
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.80,0:20:37.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这羁绊可没有时限Death
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.43,0:20:46.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就想突破蒂福日城的防线吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.43,0:20:46.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs42\fnA-OTF Kumoya Std R\b0\pos(1022.501,999)}Chateau de Tiffauges{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.10,0:20:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭你们根本无法阻拦吾
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
